Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 50年前为了抢夺四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设计让犬夜叉与桔梗自相残杀的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他收集起散落的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今妖力越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师因奈落之诅咒 在右手留下了一个风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 会将自己吞噬的风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 弥勒必须打倒奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚则是亲眼看着父亲与除妖师的同伴们被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这皆因奈落卑鄙地操纵了她的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不弄脏自己双手的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我们一定要消灭他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐之舞与神无之镜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那个叫神乐的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是从奈落身上生出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该有这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫奈落的应该是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人怎么可能生出女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落本来就是妖怪聚集而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把她想像成是分裂出来的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说是奈落本人变的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们的事也太不了解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不管她是什么样的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要想起她是奈落的一部分我就敬谢不敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又不是在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点吧 弥勒一族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 要产生风太容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟奈落有同样气味的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人背后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有跟奈落一样的蜘蛛形状的烧伤痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你们不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫神乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是女人但妖力不比寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能创造出这样的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他以前从来没有这样做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是他之前不这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是现在才有能力这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落又有了新的能力是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你承受了铁碎牙的那一击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总算能够看清楚那把刀的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在再去一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经派出了你的姐姐 神无了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那野丫头跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢反抗油老爷的公子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小春那个丫头之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先给我打断她的手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是小春没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想问你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来应该只是普通的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女的不是小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮 带她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点乖乖就范
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢不从的话 别怪我们手下不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 那个女孩危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是老大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少…少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起我们错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷 您振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷的脸被打歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙搞什么鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是来追你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 我好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我们在哪里见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是那时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们3年没见了 弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 你变得我都不认识了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真叫人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩子是弥勒的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好像根本就是朋友以上的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在战争中失去了父母跟兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被油老爷捡回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从早到晚有做不完的苦工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又饿又累的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都以泪洗面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时侯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有到村子里来驱邪的弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我最温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫做小春对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年几岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以为我生小孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…为何你们要后退？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然连小孩子都不放过！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禽兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要负责哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我还没有碰过小春分毫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那时还只是孩子嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 弥勒大人很快就离开村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天他会回来接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直是这么相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最近油老爷的公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时常用很恶心的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他终于想强行将我占有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就逃了出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用木柴打他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁他不能动的时侯逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 请您带我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无处可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以为弥勒大人生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明年纪比我还小…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然战国时代的女孩子很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 你应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能带那个女孩一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我们也不能把她留在这不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在帮她找到一个安全的栖身之所前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须留在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家也是愿意给你生小孩的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我对遇到的每个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会提出这样的要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没对我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 珊瑚 你愿意为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人是你的初恋情人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有忘记过他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信一定能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这么想 不管多苦我都能忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在觉得好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算死了也没有任何的遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那真是个可怜的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能收留她在这个村子里吗 村长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把她交给我吧 法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会给大家添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们在一起很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就死了心留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经跟村长商量过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 我们好不容易再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却马上又要分开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要谅解我 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是遇到战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知能否保护你的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在追寻的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个很可怕的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟你分开我也很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那是在说服那女孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去像打情骂俏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了他 拖泥带水的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样只会让小春对他更留恋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是我想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你从刚才开始就好像有点紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请至少让我跟您在相处一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然小春都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢 就留下来过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我再久留的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让小春更添相思之苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚就再跟她倾述一下离别之情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且小春对这座村庄还很陌生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不小心让小春怀了宝宝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春会怀念我的面容一辈子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心让小春怀宝宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 那是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最怕的就是眼泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我们明天天亮才离开村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 明天不能再哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热水的温度可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为了弥勒大人施展我全部手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全心全意做一顿晚餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些炖菜真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春真是坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了讨弥勒法师的欢心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力地做了料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得小春为我们做这顿晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕没有办法趁热吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有妖怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们出去看看再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他们离开村子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们全杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是村里的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被什么控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 他们都是普通人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人数好像很多 我也去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？小春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪突然出现 把村长大人他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖怪干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你有看到那是什么样的妖怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我只稍微看到了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉说并没有闻到妖怪的气味啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你要不要紧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女孩是妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 要手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些村民被人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要伤害到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去没完没了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你们也太天真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气杀光不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们再也爬不起来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 要是你们真能把对他们下手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就该动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你控制这些村民的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有灵魂的人跟死人也没什么两样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有灵魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那个叫戈薇的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂也已经被吸走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说 这里还有另外一个妖怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 拔出铁碎牙吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可不会像上次那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 你快回到戈薇他们那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在这解决这个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 云母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 我好怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕 已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你想对戈薇怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.26,OP,,0,0,0,,
